latestPosts.caption:
You see the videos when I work
You see the BTS 
You feel I'm living the life, but i'm just working towards a dream that I've dreamt off since the begining and have been working hard (not lucky) !

Nothing in this entire world would make me feel less than a winner when I win ! It amounts to a lot of hardworking days, Sleepless nights & early mornings
There are days when I wake up and i don't even have the energy to smile but still I do coz I wanna win 🏆

My life revolves around me meeting an enormous amount of new people daily.
Even if I have a really bad day, I make sure i smile through it. Not neccesarily faking it but just making sure that people feel better around me. You never know who is going through unknown battles.
So the next time you feel that I am going places, I've worked really hard for it.

With all the hard work and consistency theoughout years (& a lots and lots of contemplating) I've finallly decided to start something big. 
Something worth the small step but something with the intention to be bigg, bigger and if not the biggest, the best out there !

@sociography_ 
I present to you my own production house where we cater not just to clients, But also to individuals and other agencies !
With a small team of 3 currently, I'm willing to expand as an when the time prevails ! 
As for now, All i can ask is to keep us in faith and we shall deliver the best to you !

All hearts and love🎥
We are excited to announce the launch of our new project! #newproject 🙏🏼🧿
